item.title: Error, Ego, Humility and Music: A Discussion with Tony Monaco
item.description: For today’s episode we welcome jazz organist Tony Monaco to the show. Tony is a master of the Hammond B3 and has collaborated with many other great jazz musicians, including fellow jazz organist Joey DeFrancesco, drummer Steve Smith, as well as guitarists Pat Martino and George Benson, among many others... Feed: https://feeds.megaphone.fm/LIT1985735353
